Fortunately, the police intervened.  TO FLEE FOR THE WELL-BEING AND RESPECT OF YOUR CHILDREN!!!!!
I just asked if the ride was open, a completely out of sorts gentleman sent me wandering. No worries, we're going somewhere else, eh. And happy Sunday.
